description:
I would like this food so much more had I not just dropped a whole container of it on my kitchen floor and had it splatter all over my walls, and in cleanup had to discover the stuff is much greasier than I thought and stains your fridge and baseboards......

but enough about my act of clumsiness, lets talk about the food;

Decent enough Indian cuisine. Ive had better, Ive had worse, but they deliver to my hood so I am sure I will be eating more in the future. They could kick up the spicy a notch. They say you can order it hot but I never really notice the difference betwwen the hot and mild. I'm beginning to think the "pick your heat" is a sham, sad.
